ject.\n   140\t\n   141\tWhen capture is given an explicit association target, write only this\n   142\trelationship reference:\n   143\t\n   144\t```text\n   145\t<branch/change/commit target>\n   146\t  gitbutler:agent-sessions = set<session-key>\n   147\t```\n   148\t\n   149\tSee [Future Use Cases](future-use-cases.md) for access patterns and product\n   150\tmotivation.\n   151\t\n   152\t## Publication\n   153\t\n   154\tThe POC writes shareable-ready keys but does not publish them. GitMeta\n   155\tserialization, push, fetch, and sync require a later privacy and product\n   156\tdecision.\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-11T14:17:10.071Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}